node.text:
No name Thursday feature!  Simply stunning. 💫 Thanks for tagging #archi_ologie Posted @withregram • @doorwaysofchicago 🏠
➕WORKERS COTTAGE WEDNESDAY➕
📍N. Lincoln Park West - Oldtown Triangle

Although it looks like a workers cottage, what you'll discover on my Oldtown Triangle Walking Tour is that this is the only original farmhouse standing from when this area was still all farmland in the mid to late 1800's!

Learn about this and tons of other fascinating pieces of Chicago history, plus see over 40 of these darling workers cottages by coming along on my tour…click the link in my bio for tickets…4 different dates left for July! 

Leave a comment or message me with questions. 
🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠🏠
